OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings 50 years on:
OL,4,CFamilies demand public inquiry
OL,6,FFamilies of the victims of the
OL,7,Fbombings are calling on the government
OL,8,Fto launch a public inquiry into the
OL,9,Fatrocity, on the 50th anniversary of
OL,10,Fthe attacks, as ITV News' Ben Chapman
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FRelatives of people killed in the
OL,14,FBirmingham pub bombings have called
OL,15,Ffor a public inquiry on the 50th
OL,16,Fanniversary of the biggest unsolved
OL,17,Fmass murder in modern British history.
