OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings 50 years on:
OL,4,CFamilies demand public inquiry
OL,6,FTwenty-one people were killed and more
OL,7,Fthan 200 injured when two bombs
OL,8,Fexploded minutes apart in two city-
OL,9,Fcentre pubs in November 1974.
OL,11,FThe IRA is thought to have been
OL,12,Fresponsible, despite never claiming
OL,13,Fresponsibility.
OL,15,FSix men, who became known as the
OL,16,F'Birmingham Six,' were wrongly
OL,17,Fconvicted of murder but cleared in
OL,18,F1991.
OL,20,FNo one has since been charged in
OL,21,Fconnection with the attacks.
