OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings 50 years on:
OL,4,CFamilies demand public inquiry
OL,6,FFor the families of those killed, the
OL,7,Fabsence of justice has only compounded
OL,8,Fdecades of pain.
OL,10,F"It's not gone away," says Pauline
OL,11,FCurzon, whose 19-year-old sister,
OL,12,FPamela Palmer, was killed while
OL,13,Fenjoying an evening out with her
OL,14,Fboyfriend.
OL,16,F"She'd sat down near the jukebox,
OL,17,Fwhich is where they think the bomb had
OL,18,Fbeen placed," Pauline said.
