OL,6,F"The fact that it's unsolved, it
OL,7,Fdoesn't give you any peace of mind. I
OL,8,Ffeel a bit cynical. I think they know.
OL,9,FBut they're not going to tell us."
OL,11,FBy 'they,' Pauline means the British
OL,12,Fstate, which she and many of the other
OL,13,Ffamilies suspect of withholding
OL,14,Finformation about the bombings for
OL,15,Fdecades, including about whether it
OL,16,Fcould have been prevented.
