OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings 50 years on:
OL,4,CFamilies demand public inquiry
OL,6,FAfter years of campaigning, they
OL,7,Fsecured inquests into the 21 deaths in
OL,8,F2019, only to be disappointed by what
OL,9,Fthey saw as the limited scope of the
OL,10,Fhearings.
OL,12,FNow Julie Hambleton, who founded the
OL,13,F'Justice 4 the 21' group, believes
OL,14,Fonly a statutory public inquiry will
OL,15,Fforce the disclosure of secret
OL,16,Fdocuments.
