OL,6,F"Who did it? How long have you known?
OL,7,FWhy didn't you act? Did you have any
OL,8,Fpre-warnings?" are among the
OL,9,F"cacophony" of questions Julie has for
OL,10,Fthe police and British state.
OL,12,F"We will not go away," she says,
OL,13,F"until we have that for our loved ones
OL,14,Fand the survivors."
OL,16,FIn recent years, the names of
OL,17,Fpotential suspects have begun to
OL,18,Femerge.
