OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings 50 years on:
OL,4,CFamilies demand public inquiry
OL,6,FAt the inquests in 2019, a convicted
OL,7,FIRA bomber known as "Witness O" named
OL,8,Ffour of the men responsible as Seamus
OL,9,FMcLoughlin, Mick Murray, James Gavin
OL,10,Fand Michael Hayes.
OL,12,FOf those, only Michael Hayes is still
OL,13,Falive. Following the inquests, he told
OL,14,FITV News: "I didn't do it."
OL,16,FIn 2018, an ITV Exposure documentary
OL,17,Fidentified a man living in Belfast,
OL,18,FMichael Patrick Reilly, as a potential
OL,19,Fsuspect. He strongly denies any
OL,20,Finvolvement in the bombings.
